        h2.db.pt3.pt0-m.f3 Opt Out/Corrections
        .lh-copy.mb3.f4.tj-m Upon your request, We will (a) correct or update your personal information; (b) stop sending emails to your email address; and/or (c) disable your account to prevent any future purchases through that account. You can make these requests by emailing Us at <a href="mailto:contact@coinfi.com">contact@coinfi.com</a>.
        .lh-copy.mb3.f4.tj-m Please do not email your credit-card number or other sensitive information.

section.phr.pt3.bg-white.tiber
