        h2.db.pt3.pt0-m.f3 Offline Collection Use and Disclosure
        .lh-copy.mb3.f4.tj-m We also may collect information offline. We will treat any information collected offline in a manner that is consistent with this Policy.  One example involves someone calling Us to place an order or to ask questions. When someone calls, We will ask only for the personal information We need in order to place the order or to answer the question. When We need to store information (such as order information), We will enter it into our database.

