        h2.db.pt3.pt0-m.f3 Updates to this Policy
        .lh-copy.mb3.f4.tj-m If We change or update this Privacy Policy, We will post changes and updates on the Site so that you will always be aware of what information We collect, use and disclose. We encourage you to review this Policy from time to time so you will know if the Privacy Policy has been changed or updated. If you have any questions about the Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@coinfi.com">contact@coinfi.com</a>.
